These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, malaysian, japanese, spanish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, adventure, animation, spy
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the japanese##1
2. the italian is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the spanish is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
5. the italian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Nationality   | italian | malaysian | spanish | japanese |
| Movie-Genre        | epic | adventure   | spy | animation    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, cucumber, corn, garlic
House: ranch-style, townhouse, farmhouse, victorian
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
2. the ranch-style house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
3. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4
4. the ranch-style house is the person eating raspberry##1
5. the townhouse house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
6. the ranch-style house is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Food   | corn | raspberry  | cucumber  | garlic |
| House   | victorian    | ranch-style | farmhouse | townhouse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
House: art-deco, palace, wooden, cape-cod
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, singing, photography, hiking
1. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
2. the wooden house is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the palace house##3
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
6. the palace house is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| House          | cape-cod | wooden | palace    | art-deco      |
| Hobby   | photography        | hiking     | collecting | singing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee, juice, milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, pall-mall, aristoff, fonseca
1. the person drinking coffee is between the dunhill-smoker and the fonseca-smoker##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Beverage         | milk | tea | coffee | juice |
| Cigar   | aristoff       | dunhill   | pall-mall    | fonseca  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, jet-ski, skateboard, helicopter
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, video-games, reading, skydiving
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Transport   | jet-ski  | scooter    | skateboard   | helicopter       |
| Hobby   | fishing | skydiving | reading | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, bird, mouse, goldfish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, daisy, begonia, iris
1. the person who growsdaisy is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growstulip is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Pet   | mouse      | bird | goldfish | rabbit |
| Flower   | iris | daisy     | tulip  | begonia  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, collecting, woodworking, rock-climbing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, february, march, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby   | fishing | rock-climbing | woodworking | collecting    |
| Birthday     | december | march  | july     | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, tomato, potato, pumpkin
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, card-games, traveling, singing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3
2. the person eating pumpkin is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
4. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the person eating cabbage is between the person eating pumpkin and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person eating cabbage and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
8. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person eating tomato##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Food   | tomato | cabbage      | pumpkin | potato |
| Hobby   | puzzles  | singing | card-games    | traveling            |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
House: victorian, wooden, modern, art-deco
City: paris, nizza, miami, edinburgh
1. the modern house is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
2. the victorian house is on the right of the wooden house##1
3. the person traveling to paris is between the person traveling to nizza and the modern house##2
4. the person traveling to paris is in an odd position##4
5. the modern house is the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| House   | art-deco | wooden   | victorian | modern |
| City    | edinburgh     | nizza | paris     | miami  |

