.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, drawing, skydiving, baking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, lacrosse, surfing, basketball
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby      | drawing       | skydiving   | woodworking | baking |
| Sport   | surfing | lacrosse | basketball        | skateboarding    |

