.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, satire, animation, comedy
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, begonia, iris, comedy-polo
1. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growscomedy-polo##1
4. the person who growscomedy-polo is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | comedy   | satire      | animation      |
| Flower      | begonia | iris | comedy-polo | azalea |

