.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, writing, woodworking, filmmaking
There are 4 different nationalities: british, spanish, indian, canadian
1. the indian is on the left of the british##1
2. the indian is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the spanish and the indian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
