.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-13::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rat, horse, lizard
There 4 different types of food: pepper, peas, zucchini, lettuce
1. the person eating peas is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating pepper is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
3. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
4. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating peas is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Pet   | rat | goldfish | horse | lizard  |
| Food     | peas   | pepper  | lettuce  | zucchini |

