.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, aristoff, bolivar, game
City: san-francisco, london, berlin, colone
1. the person traveling to berlin is in an odd position##4
2. the bluemaster-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the game-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Cigar   | bolivar | game | bluemaster | aristoff |
| City           | colone     | san-francisco     | berlin   | london         |

