.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, fonseca, ritmeester, chaman
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, may, november, february
1. the aristoff-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in august and the fonseca-smoker##2
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Cigar   | chaman | fonseca         | aristoff   | ritmeester |
| Birthday   | november    | may | february | august   |

