.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, architect, manager, musician
4 different games are played: whist, scrabble, domino, snooker
1. the person playing snooker is the manager##1
2. the person playing domino is the software-developer##1
3. the person playing scrabble is the musician##1
4. the manager is on the left or right of the musician##3
5. the software-developer is in an even position##4
6. the manager is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Job   | architect | software-developer | manager    | musician |
| Game   | whist   | domino  | snooker | scrabble     |

