.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, emerald, green, azure
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, monopoly, backgammon
1. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes red##1
2. the person who likes green is in an even position##4
3. the person playing canasta is the person who likes green##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
5. the person playing canasta is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing monopoly##2
6. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Color         | azure   | green | red | emerald    |
| Game   | monopoly | canasta  | backgammon     | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, light-blue, yellow, black
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, basketball, volleyball, rugby
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
3. the person who likes black is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an even position##4
7. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Color   | black | brown    | yellow       | light-blue |
| Sport       | basketball  | volleyball | rugby | cycling  |

