2. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person eating avocado##3
3. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
4. the person eating kale is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
5. the colonial house is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
6. the person eating avocado is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| House   | futuristic | ranch-style | colonial  | cape-cod |
| Food     | avocado      | papaya       | kale | pear     |

