.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, chinchilla, pony, lizard
4 different games are played: backgammon, snooker, chess, bridge
1. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
3. the person playing snooker is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person playing backgammon##2
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person playing chess is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
6. the person playing chess is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | pony   | lizard | chinchilla |
| Game   | bridge          | snooker | backgammon         | chess  |

 